list.name: Changes
list.comment:
Ensures shipping order exists before retrieval
Checks for the existence of a shipping order before attempting to retrieve it, preventing potential errors and improving data integrity.
Also, refactors the shipping order retrieval process to update and persist the shipping order information whenever it is accessed, ensuring that the data is always up-to-date.
